      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 1.99,
      "endTime": 8.13
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "How did the policeman discover that the whole thing was a joke?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 8.14,
      "endTime": 14.2,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "How",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "怎样，如何"
          },
          {
            "word": "Policeman",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "警察"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "It has never been explained why university students seem to enjoy practical jokes more than anyone else.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 14.21,
      "endTime": 22.7,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Students specialize in a particular type of practical joke: the hoax.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 22.71,
      "endTime": 28.78
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Inviting the fire brigade to put out a nonexistent fire is a crude form of deception which no self-respecting student would ever indulde in.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 28.79,
      "endTime": 39.44,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Student",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "学生"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Students often create amusing situations which are funny to everyone except the victims.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 39.45,
      "endTime": 46.92,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "When a student recently saw two workmen using a pneumatic drill outside his university,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 46.93,
      "endTime": 54.23,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Student",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "学生"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "he immediately telephoned the police and informed them that two students dressed up as workmen",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 54.24,
      "endTime": 61.19,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "were tearing up the road with a pneumatic drill.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 61.2,
      "endTime": 64.68
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "As soon as he had hung up, he went over to the workmen and told them that if a policeman ordered them to go away,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 64.69,
      "endTime": 72.69,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Policeman",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "警察"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "they were not to take him seriously.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 72.7,
      "endTime": 75.41,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "He added that a student had dressed up as a policeman and was playing all sorts of silly jokes on people.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 75.42,
      "endTime": 83.77,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Student",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "学生"
          },
          {
            "word": "Policeman",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "警察"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Both the police and the workmen were grateful to the student for this piece of advance information.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 83.78,
      "endTime": 91.57,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Student",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "学生"
          },
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The student hid in an archway nearby where he could watch and hear everything that went on.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 91.58,
      "endTime": 98.72,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Student",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "学生"
          },
          {
            "word": "Watch",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "手表"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Sure enough, a policeman arrived on the scene and politely asked the workmen to go away.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 98.73,
      "endTime": 105.74,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Policeman",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "警察"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "When he received a very rude reply from one of the workmen, he threatened to remove them by force.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 105.75,
      "endTime": 113.53,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The workmen told him to do as he pleased and the policeman telephoned for help.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 113.54,
      "endTime": 119.15,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Policeman",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "警察"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Shortly afterwards, 4 more policemen arrived and remonstrated with the workmen.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 119.16,
      "endTime": 125.78
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "As the men refused to stop working, the police attempted to seize the pneumatic drill.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 125.79,
      "endTime": 132.83
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The workmen struggled fiercely and one of them lost his temper.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 132.84,
      "endTime": 138.03,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He threatened to call the police.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 138.04,
      "endTime": 140.86
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "At this, the police pointed out ironically that this would hardly be necessary as the men were already under arrest.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 140.87,
      "endTime": 150.33,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Pretending to speak seriously, one of the workmen asked if he might make a telephone call before being taken to the station.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 150.34,
      "endTime": 159.6
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Permission was granted and a policeman accompanied him to a pay phone.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 159.61,
      "endTime": 165.08,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Policeman",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "警察"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Only when he saw that the man was actually telephoning the police did he realize that they had all been the victims of a hoax.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 165.09,
      "endTime": 170.09,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
